          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1847.-step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion and carrot have softened, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>tomato paste</strong> and <strong>dried oregano</strong> to the pan and cook for 30 sec</p>\n<p>Crumble in the <strong>chicken stock cube<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> and<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>add the<strong> chopped tomatoes</strong>, <strong>Henderson's Relish</strong> and 200ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[400ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p>\n<p>Give everything a good mix up and cook for 10-15 min or until the sauce has thickened and the sausages are cooked through</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
